Project Name: GameHub

Purpose: The Game Review Platform is a web application where users can explore, review, and manage video game reviews. Users can register, log in, browse reviews, add their own reviews, update or delete them, and discover top-rated games through an attractive and responsive interface.

Key-featured: Firebase Authentication(Email & Password and Google signIn).
Toast notifications for user actions.
Show/Hide Password functionality.
Loading spinner while authentication state is being checked.
Fully Responsive Design.

NPM Package: react
react-dom
react-router
firebase
react-icons
react-toastify
tailwindcss
daisyui
motion

https://gamehub-fleming.netlify.app/
